  "text": "Let me make a synopsis and you tell me if I am correct. All of these visits for the last 75, 000 years were for the purpose of giving to the people of Earth an understanding of the Law of One, and this way allow them to progress upward through the fourth, fifth, sixth densities. This was to be a service to Earth. The pyramids were used also in giving the Law of One in their own way. The balancing pyramids, I'm not quite sure of. Am I right so far? I am Ra. You are correct to the limits of the precision allowed by language.",
